wash_trading_evidence.description: Wash traders execute buy and sell transactions in rapid succession for the exact same amount.
wash_trading_evidence.mechanism: The trader sends SOL to the Aerodrome pool (SELL) and receives SOL back (BUY) within seconds.

methodology.description: Volume attributed by SENDER. Pool excluded. Wash = balance ratio >85%, net <15%, <10 CP, >100 SOL.
